**Playflowr** is a personal tool to analyze, organize and make sense of your music playlists â€” starting with your liked tracks.

Instead of blindly auto-sorting your music, Playflowr focuses on **analysis, transparency and user control**.  
It proposes playlists based on musical signals and listening history, without ever modifying your original library.

